  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Aava is available on a Room Only basis. The hotel have an outdoor BBQ area open between 10am-10pm everyday. There is also a Starbucks if you need your daily coffee hit.</p>
<p>Based in central Whistler you have the perfect opportunity to try the local restaurants and immerse yourself in Whistler's lively atmosphere.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Aava has everything you need for a comfortable stay in the mountains, with a modern, simple design and great communal spaces.</p>
<h2>Basecamp</h2>
<p>The hotel offers great value for money and is the perfect base to explore <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> and all the activities it has to offer. You are just a snowball's throw away from the town centre with tonnes of local restaurants, bars and shops and a short walk away from the ski lifts and gondolas.</p>
<p>You can rent a pair of snow-shoes from the front desk and head into the powder.</p>
<h2>Comfort &amp; Convenience </h2>
<p>The welcoming staff make the Aava a great place to stay. Rooms are decorated simply and have all the amenities you need for your stay.</p>
<p>After a day on the slopes, kick off your skis, board, or snow-shoes and head to the hotel's wellness area with heated pool, sauna, and hot tub with mountain views.</p>]]></description>
