  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Deluxe Studio Rooms </strong>are 23m² and sleep up to four people. These rooms can either have a King bed, two Queen size beds, or a Queen and sofa bed. If you have a preference, please request at time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>Superior King Rooms</strong> are 23m² and sleep up to two people. They have a King size bed. These rooms are only available on request. Please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are 40m² and have one Queen size bed and a double sofa bed. They can sleep up to four. These rooms are only available on request. Please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom Suites </strong>have two King size beds in two inter-connecting rooms. They are about 109m² and can sleep up to six people using an extra double sofa bed. These rooms are only available on request. Please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath/shower</li>
<li>Flat screen cable TV</li>
<li>iPod docking station</li>
<li>Tea/coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Mini-fridge</li>
<li>Black-out curtains</li>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Ironing board</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
